<note n="0598010" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0598010">（定）＋出【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0599001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0599001">故＝以【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0599002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0599002">緣邪見業故彼＝以彼邪見業【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0599003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0599003">（有）＋是【三】</note>
<note n="0599004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0599004">〔有〕－【宮】</note>
<note n="0599005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0599005">〔邊〕－【宮】</note>
<note n="0599006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0599006">次頁[01]不分卷及品【三】【宮】</note>
</p>
